r — daily at 8:00. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Email","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"69b8ed66-7d42-0be3-be75-f28eac05c95d","name":"Note: Daily Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Email\n\nShapes the item: writes `messageId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"70c3e219-a1d5-4cb5-d41d-00e55b8fb5e5","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.messageId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Slot Free? · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"7c058fd8-1195-39d9-74a7-40a7926b4491","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"838dac2f-db5a-be23-4850-933e901a39e9","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Slot Free?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $items().length === 0 || !$json.id }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Booking · ②→ Propose Alternative Slots","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"56249cac-aca4-6303-2756-3ca27357d875","name":"Note: Slot Free?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Booking\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Confirmation (Discord) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,280],"id":"930d2df9-8d82-f484-1816-22a2f2d3cf1c","name":"Note: Record Booking"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Confirmation (Discord)\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hold Until Reminder Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,280],"id":"5c43dd37-9296-85fd-77ad-aa3ffc9e56dd","name":"Note: Send Confirmation (Discord)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Propose Alternative Slots\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,880],"id":"3e015ef7-73d2-d862-2d94-0196c1d34502","name":"Note: Propose Alternative Slots"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Until Reminder Time\n\nPauses 1 hours — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Send Reminder (Discord)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"7465d948-73a5-ad2a-99fc-6d9d0e809502","name":"Note: Hold Until Reminder Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Reminder (Discord)\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Guard Non-Empty from · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"8b6ab649-41ac-63a5-1d50-7c05d08d6322","name":"Note: Send Reminder (Discord)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty from\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Send Summary to Discord","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"0ffb0efc-30e7-fc6c-6d33-c3cd0abe0f44","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty from"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Discord\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"238f2740-419e-dc0b-6ea0-c47cd138c9db","name":"Note: Send Summary to Discord"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1540],"id":"67b2fb32-1eb2-39b7-d48d-9f20f7fa7692","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"f5dd75df-adff-ae7a-b9e9-7d919edc0da9","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Remind open deals with Google Drive and Discord\n\n**Pattern:** Reminders & Follow-ups · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nRemind open deals with Google Drive and Discord. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual drip campaigns is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Stamp & Shape Email → Payload Valid? → Slot Free? → Record Booking → Send Confirmation (Discord) → Hold Until Reminder Time → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to reminders & follow-ups without manual effort\n- Anyone automating drip campaigns in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Discord webhook URL; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"dd127d64-f417-8802-c67f-51adda01a7e3","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"07be5e53-f44f-0165-e5f1-2323c4b11083","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"9ba14a70-d848-19be-a515-ca7f5fbc9955","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your drip campaigns process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"f5ec3a35-6861-d5ce-10c8-5a6f46e09bb3","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Email":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Slot Free?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Slot Free?":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Booking","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Propose Alternative Slots","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Booking":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Confirmation (Discord)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Confirmation (Discord)":{"main":[[{"node":"Hold Until Reminder Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Until Reminder Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Reminder (Discord)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Reminder (Discord)":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty from","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty from":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Discord","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Propose Alternative Slots":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Discord":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"e0638675-2dc6-48ec-8efd-305e55aecfb5","id":"FDX02299"}